//*--------------------------------------------------------------------*
//* JCL documentation standard - header block and style reference
//*--------------------------------------------------------------------*
//*
//* Job card format:
//*   //IUxxxxx JOB (FB3),'Short title',CLASS=A,MSGCLASS=H,
//*   //        NOTIFY=&SYSUID,REGION=0M,TIME=1440
//*   //*       TYPRUN=HOLD
//*
//* Header block:
//*   //*--------------------------------------------------------------------*
//*   //* JOB:   IUxxxxx
//*   //* DESC:  Purpose in sentence case (single-step jobs)
//*   //*        One continuation line per step (multi-step jobs)
//*   //* STEPS: 1-STEP1, 2-STEP2  (multi-step jobs only; omit otherwise)
//*   //* AUTH:  Your name               DATE: YYYY-MM-DD
//*   //* NOTE:  Key prerequisite or caution in sentence case
//*   //*--------------------------------------------------------------------*
//*
//* Step separator (multi-step jobs only):
//*   //*-- N: STEP DESCRIPTION ----------------------------*
//*   Trailing dashes ensure the closing * aligns to column 72
//*
//* End of job footer (all jobs):
//*   //*--------------------------------------------------------------------*
//*   //* End of Job
//*   //*--------------------------------------------------------------------*
//*
//*--------------------------------------------------------------------*
